OL,3,CHow Talking Street Signs are keeping
OL,4,Can island language alive
OL,6,FAlentou d' St Helyi, y'a des
OL,7,F'Wayfinder', des singnes auvec eune
OL,8,Fcarte de la Ville et d's informations
OL,9,Fentouor le quartchi.
OL,11,FFor those not fluent in Jerriais, new
OL,12,F'Talking Signs' in St Helier will help
OL,13,Fresidents and visitors understand and
OL,14,Fmore easily listen to Jersey's
OL,15,Ftraditional language.
OL,17,FThe above reads: "Around St Helier,
OL,18,Fthere are 'Wayfinder signs' with a map
OL,19,Fof the town and information about the
OL,20,Farea."
