OL,3,CHow Talking Street Signs are keeping
OL,4,Can island language alive
OL,6,FLaurence believes that there has been
OL,7,Fa recent revival of interest in the
OL,8,Flanguage, but said it is very
OL,9,Fdifficult to hear the language being
OL,10,Fspoken.
OL,12,FHe added: "I hope that the recordings
OL,13,Fwill help bring Jerriais to people who
OL,14,Fmight not otherwise hear it and
OL,15,Fperhaps inspire some of them to start
OL,16,Flearning the language."
